'''凯阿玛自治市'''（{{lang|en|Municipality of Kiama}}；“Kiama”又译作“凯阿马”)<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.sydney.cn/destinations/south-coast |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-03 |archive-date=2020-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522011132/https://www.sydney.cn/destinations/south-coast |dead-url=no }}</ref>是个位于[[澳洲|澳洲]][[新南威尔士州|新南威尔士州]][[伊拉瓦拉|伊拉瓦拉]]的区域，东临[[塔斯曼海|塔斯曼海]]，北邻[[殼港市|殼港市]]，南靠{{link-en|肖爾黑文市|City of Shoalhaven|肖爾黑文}}，西倚[[温哲卡利比郡|温哲卡利比郡]]。辖下地方有凯阿玛（Kiama）、[[格力宫|格力宫]](Gerringong)与[[詹伯茹|占布鲁]](Jamberoo)等。其中最大市镇名也叫凯阿玛，二零一九年时，人口大概一万三千。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://kiama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/KIAMA_Chinese_brochure_2019.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-07-26 |archive-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327151951/https://kiama.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/KIAMA_Chinese_brochure_2019.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

该处著名的凯阿玛海岸步道，长约廿二公里，是条海景秀丽的远足径。凯阿玛的[[凱阿瑪噴水洞|凱阿瑪噴水洞]]，乃全地球同类结构之中最大的，每年吸引九十万访客参观。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hk.sydney.com/destinations/south-coast/kiama-area/kiama/attractions/kiama-blowhole |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-07-26 |archive-date=2018-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180114062659/https://hk.sydney.com/destinations/south-coast/kiama-area/kiama/attractions/kiama-blowhole |dead-url=no }}</ref>格力宮的维力海滩兩端均设有[[礁岩浪點|礁岩浪點]]，更有个海邊營地和所青年旅舍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hk.sydney.com/things-to-do/beach-lifestyle/south-coast-beaches |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-07-26 |archive-date=2020-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616080603/https://hk.sydney.com/things-to-do/beach-lifestyle/south-coast-beaches |dead-url=no }}</ref>占布鲁则有占布魯水上公園，內设机动玩意，目标顾客为家庭旅客。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hk.sydney.com/things-to-do/family-holidays |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-07-26 |archive-date=2020-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529063043/https://hk.sydney.com/things-to-do/family-holidays |dead-url=no }}</ref>

